

Training data 
===============
cd /home/ubuntu/fish/darknet/FISH/JPEGImages/train-all
mkdir FISH
cp ALB/* FISH/
cp BET/* FISH/
cp DOL/* FISH/
cp LAG/* FISH/
cp OTHER/* FISH/
cp SHARK/* FISH/
cp YFT/* FISH/
# rm -rf ALB BET DOL LAG NoF OTHER SHARK YFT
cd /home/ubuntu/fish/darknet/FISH/labels/train-all
mkdir FISH
cp ALB/* FISH/
cp BET/* FISH/
cp DOL/* FISH/
cp LAG/* FISH/
cp OTHER/* FISH/
cp SHARK/* FISH/
cp YFT/* FISH/

find /home/ubuntu/fish/darknet -name train.txt -exec sed -i "s/ALB/FISH/g" {} \;
find /home/ubuntu/fish/darknet -name train.txt -exec sed -i "s/BET/FISH/g" {} \;
find /home/ubuntu/fish/darknet -name train.txt -exec sed -i "s/DOL/FISH/g" {} \;
find /home/ubuntu/fish/darknet -name train.txt -exec sed -i "s/LAG/FISH/g" {} \;
find /home/ubuntu/fish/darknet -name train.txt -exec sed -i "s/OTHER/FISH/g" {} \;
find /home/ubuntu/fish/darknet -name train.txt -exec sed -i "s/SHARK/FISH/g" {} \;
find /home/ubuntu/fish/darknet -name train.txt -exec sed -i "s/YFT/FISH/g" {} \;


Set up testing data labels. 
===========================
python voc_label_FISH1.py ... to write out new train labels, all to folder FISH and all with class 0. 
#cp train-all.txt darknet/train.txt 
#cp test.txt darknet/test.txt 

Change files:
1 yolo-voc.cfg  change line classes=20, change height and width, change filters to 7 from 20
2 voc.data -> voc.FISH.data  change line classes=20
3 voc.names -> voc.FISH.names  number of lines must be equal the number of classes
4 coco.c ... change the class names and the number of classes variable
	char *coco_classes
	int coco_ids
5 yolo.c ... 

Get test images:
	mkdir tmp
	cp ../data/fish/test_stg1/img_01168.jpg tmp/tmp1.jpg
	cp ../data/fish/test_stg1/img_01177.jpg tmp/tmp2.jpg
	cp ../data/fish/test_stg1/img_01188.jpg tmp/tmp3.jpg
	cp ../data/fish/test_stg1/img_01198.jpg tmp/tmp4.jpg
	cp ../data/fish/test_stg1/img_01179.jpg tmp/tmp5.jpg

Start off a notebook so you can look at the images outputted :
	nohup jupyter notebook &
	./darknet detect cfg/yolo.cfg yolo.weights data/dog.jpg

Change cudnn to 1 and remake
Train:
	./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH.data cfg/yolo-voc.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 
	./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 


To predict :
Change cudnn to 0 and remake
#./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH.data cfg/yolo-voc.cfg backup/yolo-voc_13000.weights 
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
And then check under results folder
then try 
	grep "img_07050" *
# ./darknet detector test cfg/voc.FISH.data cfg/yolo-voc.cfg backup/yolo-voc_3000.weights tmp/tmp1.jpg -thresh 0.1


To validate (see also https://github.com/AlexeyAB/darknet#when-should-i-stop-training) :
cp train.txt data/voc.2007.test
 ./darknet detector recall cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 3311  4282  4371	RPs/Img: 30.50	IOU: 81.20%	Recall:97.96% (11k)
# 3311  4264  4371	RPs/Img: 33.05	IOU: 80.60%	Recall:97.55% (8k)
# 3311  4249  4371	RPs/Img: 53.66	IOU: 79.15%	Recall:97.21% (5k)



# 544 x 544 Images

# Set up testing data labels @ 544 
# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# Set up testing data labels @ 544 
# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

# 544 x 544 Images

# Set up testing data labels @ 544 
# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# Set up testing data labels @ 544 
# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

# 544 x 544 Images

# Set up testing data labels @ 544 
# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# Set up testing data labels @ 544 
# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

# 544 x 544 Images

# Set up testing data labels @ 544 
# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# Set up testing data labels @ 544 
# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

# 544 x 544 Images

# Set up testing data labels @ 544 
# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# Set up testing data labels @ 544 
# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

# 544 x 544 Images

# Set up testing data labels @ 544 
# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# Set up testing data labels @ 544 
# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

# 544 x 544 Images

# Set up testing data labels @ 544 
# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# Set up testing data labels @ 544 
# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

# 544 x 544 Images

# Set up testing data labels @ 544 
# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# Set up testing data labels @ 544 
# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

# 544 x 544 Images

# Set up testing data labels @ 544 
# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# Set up testing data labels @ 544 
# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

# 544 x 544 Images

# Set up testing data labels @ 544 
# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# Set up testing data labels @ 544 
# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

# 544 x 544 Images

# Set up testing data labels @ 544 
# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# Set up testing data labels @ 544 
# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

# 544 x 544 Images

# Set up testing data labels @ 544 
# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# Set up testing data labels @ 544 
# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

# 544 x 544 Images

# Set up testing data labels @ 544 
# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&

# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# Change files:
cp cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg
mkdir backupFISH544
vim cfg/yolo-voc-FISH544.cfg  # change height and width

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights

./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# =================================

# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake

# Change cudnn to 1 and remake
# Train:
# ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 

nohup ./darknet detector train cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg darknet19_448.conv.23 > nohup544.out 2>&1&


# To predict :
# Change cudnn to 0 and remake
./darknet detector valid cfg/voc.FISH1.data cfg/yolo-voc-FISH.cfg backupFISH544/yolo-voc-FISH_11000.weights
# 544 x 544 Images

# Set up testing data labels @ 544 
# =================================

# Change files:
